3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper uses a mean-field game framework to model the power control problem, which is a technique commonly used in systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with millimeter wave networks, which are used for high-speed multimedia applications. 
5. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory): The paper uses a game-theoretic approach to model the power control problem, which falls under the scope of computer science and game theory.
